    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Amends title XIX (Medicaid) of the Social Security Act to require states to have in place a system for the electronic verification of visits conducted as part of personal care services or else have their federal medical assistance percentage reduced by specified amounts.</p>]]></text>
